    "description": "<strong>DesktopMars 仅适用于 WINDOWS 10/11。</strong><br><br>DesktopMars 是我的新项目，我在其中结合了建设性游戏和动态壁纸，全部采用 Minecraft / Voxel 的风格。<br><br>在埃隆马斯克之前建造、收集、升级和扩大你在火星上的新人口！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/427052b25167bbcd9a39bea07116f7ba.poster.avif?t=1659223092\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/427052b25167bbcd9a39bea07116f7ba.webm?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/427052b25167bbcd9a39bea07116f7ba.mp4?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/4155283ca88343e0bc5691833faf5f3b.poster.avif?t=1659223092\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/4155283ca88343e0bc5691833faf5f3b.webm?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/4155283ca88343e0bc5691833faf5f3b.mp4?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><strong>-不赶时间</strong>-按照你的风格和时间建立你的殖民地。<br><br><strong>-真正的昼夜系统</strong> - 如果你在晚上玩，你的殖民地也会在晚上。<br><br><strong>-显示为墙纸</strong> - 做其他事情时，在桌面上建立你的火星殖民地。<br><br><strong>-自动暂停</strong> - 当您玩游戏时，DesktopMars 会暂停这一刻。<br><br><strong>-Windows 自动启动</strong> - 当您运行 PC 时，您在火星上的殖民地将开始工作。<br><br><strong>-Steam 断开连接</strong> - 隐藏您的活动（需要重新启动游戏）。<br><br><strong>-Optimized</strong> - 优化以将 PC 使用率降至最低。<br><br><strong>-设置检查</strong> - 壁纸将识别您的系统设置并在需要时进行更改。如果没有，请阅读“社区中心/讨论”或给我发短信寻求帮助。<br><br><strong>-很便宜</strong> - 给我一杯咖啡。提前致谢。 ;D<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/826acd390c5a21b03a729e6e44f8989b.poster.avif?t=1659223092\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/826acd390c5a21b03a729e6e44f8989b.webm?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/826acd390c5a21b03a729e6e44f8989b.mp4?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有任何问题，请阅读 <strong>“社区 HUB / 讨论”</strong> 或给我发短信寻求帮助。如果需要，我会尽快回复并进行紧急更新。或者只是给我发短信说你好。 ;D<br><br><strong>最好的问候，</strong><br>3DM格雷格<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/93b7d79a8f06a4cdd7d8af1420cb5510.poster.avif?t=1659223092\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/93b7d79a8f06a4cdd7d8af1420cb5510.webm?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895410/extras/93b7d79a8f06a4cdd7d8af1420cb5510.mp4?t=1659223092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
